PrecisAppointment of : GASTON BARBAN as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of South Africa and as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Namibia, with residence in Pretoria; and ROBERT READY as High Commissioner for Canada to the Commonwealth of the Bahamas, with residence in Kingston.
